<INPUT TYPE="HIDDEN" NAME="survey_name" VALUE="SAO::Honors Application">
<INPUT TYPE="HIDDEN" NAME="begin_date" VALUE="2005-05-09">
<INPUT TYPE="HIDDEN" NAME="end_date" VALUE="2024-05-09">

  

  

  

  

  
  <p>Please be sure you have reviewed <a href="/ugrad/honors/index.php">the program details and eligibility requirements</a> before applying. </p>
  <p> <strong>Please submit your Bren School of ICS Honors Application by noon on Monday June, 1st.</strong></p>
  <p><strong>Please inform your 2 Bren School faculty references that they must access the reference form via the Bren School faculty intranet and submit it by June 1.</strong></p>
  <p> For further information, please contact the Bren School Student Affairs office at (949) 824-5156, or send email to <a href="mailto:ucounsel@uci.edu">ucounsel@uci.edu</a>.</p>
  </div>
